In this folder:

quotes.js: creates and connects to a MongoDB database (called quotes), creates a collection (also called quotes)
           and provides a command line interface for inserting quotes, and for finding quotes by author. 

authors.js: index's the author key in the MongoDB and retrieves distinct list of authors

quotes_votes.js: extends quotes.js with a voting mechanism, updates a selected record with a vote field, runs the 
                 MongoDB $inc modifier to increase vote by 1 (if it is already there) returns a list of the top 10
                 quotes according to highest votes. 
